Investment Strategies
Fayez Sarofim & Co. offers four types of investment strategies - Large Capitalization Equity, Global Equity, Core Fixed  Income and Balanced Portfolios. Each of these strategies has been honed over time to deliver excess returns over notable market indices by consistently applying our proven, long-term philosophy.


