About
Fayez Sarofim & Co. is located at the address 909 Fannin St in Houston, Texas 77010.  They can be contacted via phone at (713) 654-4484 for pricing, hours and directions.  Fayez Sarofim & Co. specializes in Government, Short-Term Disability, Children & Teens.  Fayez Sarofim & Co. has an annual sales volume of 50M – 99,999,999.  .For more information contact S. E. Cody Dick, Analyst or  go to www.sarofim.comFayez Sarofim & Co. provides Income Planning, Term Life Insurance, Consultations to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Fayez Sarofim & Co. view the map to the right.  For reviews of Fayez Sarofim & Co. see below.









