About
Sarofim, Fayez & Co Inc is located at the address Po Box 52830 in Houston, Texas 77052.  They can be contacted via phone at (713) 654-4484 for pricing, hours and directions.  Sarofim, Fayez & Co Inc has an annual sales volume of 20M – 49,999,999.  .For more information contact Fayez  Sarofim, President or  go to www.sarofim.comSarofim, Fayez & Co Inc provides Corporate Services, Retirement Services, Long Term Planning to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Sarofim, Fayez & Co Inc view the map to the right.  For reviews of Sarofim, Fayez & Co Inc see below.









